headline: Is Fidelity National Information Services Stock Underperforming the Dow?
summary: While Fidelity National Information Services has lagged the Dow Jones Industrial Average in recent performance, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook for the stock’s future prospects.
